Indulge in the enchanting beauty of sunsets every time you open a new tab with "Sunset Backgrounds", a Chrome extension designed to elevate your browsing experience. Experience a visual retreat as each new tab unveils a mesmerizing, high-quality image of a sunset from various beautiful locations across the world. Our carefully curated collection captures the peaceful and awe-inspiring moments of dusk, from the vibrant colors over ocean horizons to the soft hues cast over mountain ranges.
